            "Key": "Deer",
            "SourceString": "Weakness: Ranged\r\nResistance: None\r\n\r\nThe graceful deer is a skittish beast, easily frightened by the slightest sounds. On the mainland, deer are a rare sight, sticking to deep forests and areas of fairy enchantment. They were extensively hunted for their delicious meat and sturdy antlers.\r\n\r\nOn Ashenfall, magic has infused their bodies, making their pelts versatile and highly valuable. Well worth the effort of any hunter.",
